# 3. Sensor System Design (Full Module + Per-Sensor Plan)

## 🎯 Objective

Build a **functional, real-time sensor module** that:

* Lists all available sensors
* Streams live data
* Provides **basic visualization + simple interpretation**

No overdesign. Focus:

> Reliable data + clear visualization + controlled lifecycle

---

# 🏗️ Module Architecture

```text id="qz9x1l"
SensorLabActivity
    ├── Sensor List (RecyclerView)
    └── SensorDetailActivity (Dynamic UI per sensor)
```

---

# 📱 1. SensorLabActivity (Sensor List Screen)

## 🎯 Purpose:

* Discover and display all available sensors

---

## 🔧 Data Source

```java id="nqf8w2"
SensorManager sm = (SensorManager) getSystemService(SENSOR_SERVICE);
List<Sensor> sensorList = sm.getSensorList(Sensor.TYPE_ALL);
```

---

## 🧩 UI Structure

```text id="2p3zye"
RecyclerView
   ├── Accelerometer
   ├── Gyroscope
   ├── Light
   ├── Proximity
   ├── ...
```

---

## 📌 Each Item Shows:

* Sensor Name
* Sensor Type
* Vendor (optional)

---

## 🔁 On Click Flow

```text id="r1z9ak"
User taps sensor
   ↓
Open SensorDetailActivity
   ↓
Pass sensor TYPE via Intent
```

```java id="a2l4jf"
intent.putExtra("sensor_type", sensor.getType());
```

---

# 🎮 2. SensorDetailActivity (Core Engine)

## 🎯 Purpose:

* Handle **real-time data + visualization**

---

## 🔧 Setup

```java id="f9l2kd"
Sensor sensor = sm.getDefaultSensor(sensorType);
```

---

## 🎧 Listener

```java id="p0x3mz"
SensorEventListener listener = new SensorEventListener() {
    @Override
    public void onSensorChanged(SensorEvent event) {
        updateUI(event.values);
    }

    @Override
    public void onAccuracyChanged(Sensor sensor, int accuracy) {}
};
```

---

## 🔁 Lifecycle Handling

```text id="t8u2df"
onResume() → registerListener
onPause() → unregisterListener
```

---

